author: CMS-HIN-dilepton
body: This PR is meant for pPb 2016 run and it adds 3 new Z mass histograms to the Online DQM HLTObjectMonitor module. The triggers used will be included in the pPb HLT Menu (based on confdb HLT menu  /users/anstahll/PA2016/PAMuon2016/ ) and this PR is needed for our JIRA ticket.
title: Added Z mass histograms in Online DQM to monitor L1/L2/L3 dimuon triggers for pPb 2016
